 Except for a compass or other magnetic object, 

00:01:31.940 --> 00:01:36.503
 We rarely see a material that responds to a magnetic field. 

00:01:36.503 --> 00:01:40.033
 But place the plasma in an electric field or magnetic field, 

00:01:40.033 --> 00:01:42.416
 You will get a very different reaction. 

00:01:42.416 --> 00:01:44.368
 Because plasma is charged, 

00:01:44.368 --> 00:01:46.324
 Electric fields accelerate, 

00:01:46.324 --> 00:01:50.628
 The magnetic fields guide them in circular orbits. 

00:01:50.628 --> 00:01:52.918
 When the particles collide within the plasma, 

00:01:52.918 --> 00:01:56.381
 Or accelerated by electricity or magnetism, 

00:01:56.381 --> 00:01:58.119
 Light is generated, 

